    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine is currently running poorly with a noticeable misfire, and the transmission slips when shifting into higher gears. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several dents across the body. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn seats and a headliner that is sagging. It is being sold strictly as-is and is best suited for someone looking for a parts car or a dedicated restoration project.",
